  "original_title": "\u0db1\u0dc0 \u0d89\u0db1\u0dca\u0daf\u0dd3\u0dba \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0db1\u0dd2\u0dba \u0dc0\u0dd9\u0dad \u0da0\u0dd3\u0db1 \u0da2\u0db1\u0db4\u0dad\u0dd2\u0d9c\u0dd9\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd4\u0db6 \u0db4\u0dd0\u0dad\u0dd4\u0db8\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Greetings from the Chinese President to the new Indian President",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Chinese President Xi Jinping has sent a congratulatory message to Indian President Draupadi Murmu.",
        "Noting that China and India are each other's important neighbors, Xi said that a better and more stable Sino-Indian relationship would serve the basic interests of both countries and peoples, as well as be conducive to regional and world peace, stability and development.",
        "Xi said that he attaches great importance to China-India relations and is ready to work with President Murmu to improve political mutual trust, deepen practical cooperation, manage differences properly and push bilateral relations on the right track.",
        "Murmu was sworn in as the 15th President of India on Monday. She is the second President of India and the first person from India's tribal community to hold the country's highest constitutional post."
      ],
